data.description:
Lovely 3/2 Barndominium with granite countertops, high ceilings, comfortable floor plan, on 8.35 acres, and many mature trees. Two of which are approximately 100 years old. In addition, there is also another living space with a half bath that can be used as an office or apartment. 10 horse stalls, an all weather shed in the west pasture, a chicken coop, and two fruit trees. Untouched nutrient rich soil in abundance. This one is a gem, with endless possibilities and room to grow. 
Less than 10 min to downtown Elsa, 20 min to Edinburg or Weslco, 30 min to McAllen or Harlingen, One hour and 20 minutes to SPI, 2 hrs to Corpus Christi


Encantador 3/2 Barndominium con encimeras de granito, techos altos, plano de planta cómodo, en 8.35 acres y muchos árboles maduros.  Dos de los cuales tienen aproximadamente 100 años.  Además, también hay otro espacio habitable con medio baño que se puede utilizar como oficina o apartamento.  10 puestos de caballos, un cobertizo para todo clima en el pasto oeste, un gallinero y dos árboles frutales.  Suelo intacto rico en nutrientes en abundancia.  Esta es una joya, con infinitas posibilidades y espacio para crecer.
 Menos de 10 minutos al centro de Elsa, 20 minutos a Edinburg o Weslco, 30 minutos a McAllen o Harlingen, una hora y 20 minutos a SPI, 2 horas a Corpus Christi
data.whatILove:
Inside the home I appreciate the comfortable layout of the floor plan, with an open and bright living room, dining room, custom kitchen space. large bedrooms, deep closets, granite countertops, high ceilings, and beautiful views out picture windows. 
Around the home you will find plenty of space to create and grow. There are also an abundance of large, mature, Shea trees. The nature and wildlife are exceedingly enjoyable, just within the fence line. There is also every convenience, nature parks, museums, libraries, etc. within a short distance of the home.
